rom\": 273, \"to\": 279}, {\"ngram\": \"padel\", \"from\": 298, \"to\": 303}, {\"ngram\": \"just a fad\", \"from\": 307, \"to\": 317}]}, {\"sentence\": \"That seems unlikely, given the level of investment that has been pumped into what is still a relatively new sport which was invented by Enrique Corcuera in Acapulco and combines elements of tennis, squash and badminton.\", \"from\": 320, \"to\": 539, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 464, \"end\": 472, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Corcuera\", \"score\": 0.9999999999954525, \"rank\": 3.808236528326889e-12, \"text\": \"Corcuera\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Corcuera\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Corcuera\"}, {\"begin\": 476, \"end\": 484, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Acapulco\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.072456612827055e-16, \"text\": \"Acapulco\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Acapulco\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Acapulco\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the level\", \"from\": 347, \"to\": 356}, {\"ngram\": \"investment\", \"from\": 360, \"to\": 370}, {\"ngram\": \"a relatively new sport\", \"from\": 411, \"to\": 433}, {\"ngram\": \"elements\", \"from\": 498, \"to\": 506}, {\"ngram\": \"tennis\", \"from\": 510, \"to\": 516}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The Lawn Tennis Association said in September: 'Since becoming the national governing body for the sport in Britain in 2020, significant investment has already been directed towards developing and supporting padel in Britain.\", \"from\": 541, \"to\": 766, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 545, \"end\": 568, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lawn_Tennis_Association\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.8929852929169271e-19, \"text\": \"Lawn Tennis Association\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lawn_Tennis_Association\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lawn_Tennis_Association\"}, {\"begin\": 649, \"end\": 656, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"score\": 0.9999999912979547, \"rank\": 8.702109061298177e-09, \"text\": \"Britain\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\"}, {\"begin\": 758, \"end\": 765, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"score\": 0.9999999912979547, \"rank\": 8.702109061298177e-09, \"text\": \"Britain\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"September\", \"from\": 577, \"to\": 586}, {\"ngram\": \"the national governing body\", \"from\": 604, \"to\": 631}, {\"ngram\": \"the sport\", \"from\": 636, \"to\": 645}, {\"ngram\": \"significant investment\", \"from\": 666, \"to\": 688}, {\"ngram\": \"developing and supporting padel\", \"from\": 723, \"to\": 754}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'In addition to private investment, the LTA and LTA Tennis Foundation have invested \\u00a36 million into 40 padel facility projects funding a total of 75 new courts, as well as the competition structure, performance support and coach development.\", \"from\": 768, \"to\": 1009, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 808, \"end\": 811, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lawn_Tennis_Association\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 7.81330921053578e-25, \"text\": \"LTA\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lawn_Tennis_Association\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lawn_Tennis_Association\"}, {\"begin\": 816, \"end\": 819, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lawn_Tennis_Association\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 7.81330921053578e-25, \"text\": \"LTA\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lawn_Tennis_Association\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lawn_Tennis_Association\"}, {\"begin\": 820, \"end\": 826, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tennis\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.444957896460101e-28, \"text\": \"Tennis\", \"types\": [\"Q349\", \"Q1914636\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tennis\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tennis\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"addition\", \"from\": 772, \"to\": 780}, {\"ngram\": \"private investment\", \"from\": 784, \"to\": 802}, {\"ngram\": \"40 padel facility projects\", \"from\": 868, \"to\": 894}, {\"ngram\": \"a total\", \"from\": 903, \"to\": 910}, {\"ngram\": \"75 new courts\", \"from\": 914, \"to\": 927}, {\"ngram\": \"the competition structure\", \"from\": 940, \"to\": 965}, {\"ngram\": \"performance support\", \"from\": 967, \"to\": 986}, {\"ngram\": \"coach development\", \"from\": 991, \"to\": 1008}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'In total, since 2019 the number of courts has grown from 50 to 350, annual participation from 6,000 to 129,000, and the LTA has launched new coaching courses, as well as a performance pathway to support Britain's best players.'\", \"from\": 1011, \"to\": 1239, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1132, \"end\": 1135, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lawn_Tennis_Association\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 7.81330921053578e-25, \"text\": \"LTA\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lawn_Tennis_Association\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lawn_Tennis_Association\"}, {\"begin\": 1215, \"end\": 1222, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"score\": 0.9999999912979547, \"rank\": 8.702109061298177e-09, \"text\": \"Britain\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"total\", \"from\": 1015, \"to\": 1020}, {\"ngram\": \"the number\", \"from\": 1033, \"to\": 1043}, {\"ngram\": \"courts\", \"from\": 1047, \"to\": 1053}, {\"ngram\": \"new coaching courses\", \"from\": 1149, \"to\": 1169}, {\"ngram\": \"a performance pathway\", \"from\": 1182, \"to\": 1203}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Critics, meanwhile, have complained that it's too loud, or too hard to get four people together - given that padel is mainly played in doubles - and the people who truly love it, likeJason Manford, are worried it's in danger of lurching towards elitism.\", \"from\": 1241, \"to\": 1494, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Critics\", \"from\": 1241, \"to\": 1248}, {\"ngram\": \"four people\", \"from\": 1316, \"to\": 1327}, {\"ngram\": \"that padel\", \"from\": 1345, \"to\": 1355}, {\"ngram\": \"doubles\", \"from\": 1376, \"to\": 1383}, {\"ngram\": \"danger\", \"from\": 1459, \"to\": 1465}, {\"ngram\": \"elitism\", \"from\": 1486, \"to\": 1493}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Away from the world ofcomedy, Manford, a self-confessed padel addict who moved across from tennis after a shoulder injury, is on a personal mission to help grow this unique game.\", \"from\": 1496, \"to\": 1674, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the world ofcomedy\", \"from\": 1506, \"to\": 1524}, {\"ngram\": \"Manford\", \"from\": 1526, \"to\": 1533}, {\"ngram\": \"a self-confessed padel addict\", \"from\": 1535, \"to\": 1564}, {\"ngram\": \"tennis\", \"from\": 1587, \"to\": 1593}, {\"ngram\": \"a shoulder injury\", \"from\": 1600, \"to\": 1617}, {\"ngram\": \"a personal mission\", \"from\": 1625, \"to\": 1643}, {\"ngram\": \"this unique game\", \"from\": 1657, \"to\": 1673}]}, {\"sentence\": \"While this professional funny man may tell jokes for a living, when it comes to padel, he is nothing but serious.\", \"from\": 1675, \"to\": 1788, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"this professional funny man\", \"from\": 1681, \"to\": 1708}, {\"ngram\": \"jokes\", \"from\": 1718, \"to\": 1723}, {\"ngram\": \"a living\", \"from\": 1728, \"to\": 1736}, {\"ngram\": \"padel\", \"from\": 1755, \"to\": 1760}, {\"ngram\": \"nothing\", \"from\": 1768, \"to\": 1775}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Despite impressive growth, though, Great Britain failed to enter a team at the last world youth championships.\", \"from\": 1790, \"to\": 1900, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1825, \"end\": 1838, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"score\": 0.9999997742670784, \"rank\": 2.240443936892355e-07, \"text\": \"Great Britain\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"impressive growth\", \"from\": 1798, \"to\": 1815}, {\"ngram\": \"a team\", \"from\": 1855, \"to\": 1861}, {\"ngram\": \"the last world youth championships\", \"from\": 1865, \"to\": 1899}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Meanwhile, the founder of a new club inLondonvows he's learnt from the key mistakes made in his home country ofSweden.\", \"from\": 1901, \"to\": 2019, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the founder\", \"from\": 1912, \"to\": 1923}, {\"ngram\": \"a new club\", \"from\": 1927, \"to\": 1937}, {\"ngram\": \"the key mistakes\", \"from\": 1968, \"to\": 1984}, {\"ngram\": \"his home country\", \"from\": 1993, \"to\": 2009}]}, {\"sentence\": \"With plenty to unpack, and Manford's 'dream' for Brisbane 2032,Metrotook a deep dive into the curious world of padel.\", \"from\": 2021, \"to\": 2138, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"plenty\", \"from\": 2026, \"to\": 2032}, {\"ngram\": \"Manford's 'dream\", \"from\": 2048, \"to\": 2064}, {\"ngram\": \"Brisbane 2032,Metrotook\", \"from\": 2070, \"to\": 2093}, {\"ngram\": \"the curious world\", \"from\": 2111, \"to\": 2128}, {\"ngram\": \"padel\", \"from\": 2132, \"to\": 2137}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Here's what we found\\u2026 Earlier this year, Djokovic warned that club tennis is 'endangered' amid the growing popularity of alternatives such as padel in Europe andpickleballin the United States.\", \"from\": 2139, \"to\": 2332, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2181, \"end\": 2189, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Novak_Djokovic\", \"score\": 0.999999999998181, \"rank\": 1.5332722848535613e-12, \"text\": \"Djokovic\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Novak_Djokovic\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Novak_Djokovic\"}, {\"begin\": 2318, \"end\": 2331, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"score\": 0.9999995071795034, \"rank\": 4.922852589536941e-07, \"text\": \"United States\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"club tennis\", \"from\": 2201, \"to\": 2212}, {\"ngram\": \"the growing popularity\", \"from\": 2234, \"to\": 2256}, {\"ngram\": \"alternatives\", \"from\": 2260, \"to\": 2272}, {\"ngram\": \"padel\", \"from\": 2281, \"to\": 2286}, {\"ngram\": \"Europe\", \"from\": 2290, \"to\": 2296}]}, {\"sentence\": \"There issometruth in that.\", \"from\": 2334, \"to\": 2360, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"There issometruth\", \"from\": 2334, \"to\": 2351}]}, {\"sentence\": \"If you are of a certain age and have suffered injuries, then padel may make more sense to you than tennis.\", \"from\": 2361, \"to\": 2467, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a certain age\", \"from\": 2375, \"to\": 2388}, {\"ngram\": \"injuries\", \"from\": 2407, \"to\": 2415}, {\"ngram\": \"padel\", \"from\": 2422, \"to\": 2427}, {\"ngram\": \"more sense\", \"from\": 2437, \"to\": 2447}, {\"ngram\": \"tennis\", \"from\": 2460, \"to\": 2466}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It has a less strenuous impact on the body, a smaller court and it's easier to play.\", \"from\": 2468, \"to\": 2552, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a less strenuous impact\", \"from\": 2475, \"to\": 2498}, {\"ngram\": \"the body\", \"from\": 2502, \"to\": 2510}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Plus, new clubs are popping up everywhere.\", \"from\": 2553, \"to\": 2595, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"new clubs\", \"from\": 2559, \"to\": 2568}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'For a lot of my mates, who are in their 50s and want to be active but can not afford to break their ankles, it's perfect,' Manford toldMetro.\", \"from\": 2597, \"to\": 2739, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a lot\", \"from\": 2602, \"to\": 2607}, {\"ngram\": \"my mates\", \"from\": 2611, \"to\": 2619}, {\"ngram\": \"their 50s\", \"from\": 2632, \"to\": 2641}, {\"ngram\": \"their ankles\", \"from\": 2692, \"to\": 2704}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'I injured my rotator cuff on my left shoulder.\", \"from\": 2740, \"to\": 2787, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"my rotator cuff\", \"from\": 2751, \"to\": 2766}, {\"ngram\": \"my left shoulder\", \"from\": 2770, \"to\": 2786}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I am left-handed.\", \"from\": 2788, \"to\": 2805, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"So serving was just killing me, it was so painful.\", \"from\": 2806, \"to\": 2856, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"'If you are 60, you are probably not going to pick up a tennis racket now.\", \"from\": 2858, \"to\": 2932, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a tennis racket\", \"from\": 2912, \"to\": 2927}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Whereas you could quite easily pick up a padel racket and play.'\", \"from\": 2933, \"to\": 2997, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a padel racket\", \"from\": 2972, \"to\": 2986}, {\"ngram\": \"play\", \"from\": 2991, \"to\": 2995}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Samuel De Haan, the founder of Square One Padel in Kent, said: 'If you are 50, 60+, we have a lot of members at our club who have come from tennis purely because they are getting injured.\", \"from\": 2999, \"to\": 3186, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3006, \"end\": 3013, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Foppe_de_Haan\", \"score\": 0.9999999984229362, \"rank\": 1.577465222813358e-09, \"text\": \"De Haan\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q628099\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Foppe_de_Haan\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Foppe_de_Haan\"}, {\"begin\": 3030, \"end\": 3040, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Square_One_Television\", \"score\": 0.999999995359758, \"rank\": 4.640119154756543e-09, \"text\": \"Square One\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\", \"Q15416\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Square_One_Television\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Square_One_Television\"}, {\"begin\": 3041, \"end\": 3046, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Padel_(sport)\", \"score\": 0.9869493094630484, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Padel\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Padel_(sport)\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Padel_(sport)\"}, {\"begin\": 3050, \"end\": 3054, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kent\", \"score\": 0.9999999830597518, \"rank\": 1.6940692166588283e-08, \"text\": \"Kent\", \"types\": [\"Q3455524\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kent\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kent\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the founder\", \"from\": 3015, \"to\": 3026}, {\"ngram\": \"a lot\", \"from\": 3091, \"to\": 3096}, {\"ngram\": \"members\", \"from\": 3100, \"to\": 3107}, {\"ngram\": \"our club\", \"from\": 3111, \"to\": 3119}, {\"ngram\": \"tennis\", \"from\": 3139, \"to\": 3145}]}, {\"sentence\": \"They are struggling with hip pain, back pain, playing on a big court and struggling to move around it.'\", \"from\": 3187, \"to\": 3290, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"hip pain\", \"from\": 3212, \"to\": 3220}, {\"ngram\": \"back pain\", \"from\": 3222, \"to\": 3231}, {\"ngram\": \"a big court\", \"from\": 3244, \"to\": 3255}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But the myth that padel is slowly going to take over and replace tennis is farfetched.\", \"from\": 3292, \"to\": 3378, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the myth\", \"from\": 3296, \"to\": 3304}, {\"ngram\": \"padel\", \"from\": 3310, \"to\": 3315}, {\"ngram\": \"tennis\", \"from\": 3357, \"to\": 3363}]}, {\"sentence\": \"If anything, it acts as an introduction to racket sports for most children.\", \"from\": 3379, \"to\": 3454, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"an introduction\", \"from\": 3403, \"to\": 3418}, {\"ngram\": \"racket sports\", \"from\": 3422, \"to\": 3435}, {\"ngram\": \"most children\", \"from\": 3440, \"to\": 3453}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'We do not see ourselves as competing with tennis,' Sebastian Gordon, the founder of Rocket Padel at Battersea Power Station, said.\", \"from\": 3456, \"to\": 3587, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3508, \"end\": 3517, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Timbaland\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 5.169557999135349e-20, \"text\": \"Sebastian\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Timbaland\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Timbaland\"}, {\"begin\": 3518, \"end\": 3524, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mike_Gordon\", \"score\": 0.8877413606615441, \"rank\": 0.1264542176155043, \"text\": \"Gordon\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q483501\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mike_Gordon\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mike_Gordon\"}, {\"begin\": 3548, \"end\": 3553, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Padel_(sport)\", \"score\": 0.9869493094630484, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Padel\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Padel_(sport)\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Padel_(sport)\"}, {\"begin\": 3557, \"end\": 3580, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Battersea_Power_Station\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 4.8466142971163616e-26, \"text\": \"Battersea Power Station\", \"types\": [\"Q159719\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Battersea_Power_Station\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Battersea_Power_Station\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"tennis\", \"from\": 3499, \"to\": 3505}, {\"ngram\": \"the founder\", \"from\": 3526, \"to\": 3537}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'We are competing with restaurants, cinemas, Netflix, yoga and CrossFit.\", \"from\": 3588, \"to\": 3660, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3633, \"end\": 3640, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Netflix\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 7.599814392057407e-19, \"text\": \"Netflix\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Netflix\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Netflix\"}, {\"begin\": 3651, \"end\": 3659, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/CrossFit\", \"score\": 0.999999999996362, \"rank\": 4.021672469612724e-12, \"text\": \"CrossFit\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/CrossFit\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/CrossFit\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"restaurants\", \"from\": 3611, \"to\": 3622}, {\"ngram\": \"cinemas\", \"from\": 3624, \"to\": 3631}, {\"ngram\": \"yoga\", \"from\": 3642, \"to\": 3646}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The sport is social and it's a low barrier to entry.\", \"from\": 3661, \"to\": 3713, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The sport\", \"from\": 3661, \"to\": 3670}, {\"ngram\": \"a low barrier\", \"from\": 3690, \"to\": 3703}, {\"ngram\": \"entry\", \"from\": 3707, \"to\": 3712}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It's very easy to learn.\", \"from\": 3714, \"to\": 3738, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I do not really look at tennis and compare it.'\", \"from\": 3739, \"to\": 3786, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"tennis\", \"from\": 3763, \"to\": 3769}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'For a young kid I think padel is a gateway to tennis and other racket sports,' Manford added.\", \"from\": 3788, \"to\": 3882, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a young kid\", \"from\": 3793, \"to\": 3804}, {\"ngram\": \"padel\", \"from\": 3813, \"to\": 3818}, {\"ngram\": \"a gateway\", \"from\": 3822, \"to\": 3831}, {\"ngram\": \"tennis\", \"from\": 3835, \"to\": 3841}, {\"ngram\": \"other racket sports\", \"from\": 3846, \"to\": 3865}, {\"ngram\": \"Manford\", \"from\": 3868, \"to\": 3875}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'You can pick it up and play it straight away.\", \"from\": 3883, \"to\": 3929, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"And if you are really good at it, you can start playing proper tennis!\", \"from\": 3930, \"to\": 4000, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"proper tennis\", \"from\": 3986, \"to\": 3999}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Then you can make some money and go pro or whatever.\", \"from\": 4001, \"to\": 4053, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"some money\", \"from\": 4019, \"to\": 4029}]}, {\"sentence\": \"That's how I see it, rather than being a rival to tennis.'\", \"from\": 4054, \"to\": 4112, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a rival\", \"from\": 4093, \"to\": 4100}, {\"ngram\": \"tennis\", \"from\": 4104, \"to\": 4110}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Manford, a proud Mancunian, is concerned about padel falling into the trap of elitism.\", \"from\": 4114, \"to\": 4200, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4131, \"end\": 4140, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Manchester\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 8.406996787280742e-21, \"text\": \"Mancunian\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Manchester\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Manchester\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Manford\", \"from\": 4114, \"to\": 4121}, {\"ngram\": \"padel\", \"from\": 4161, \"to\": 4166}, {\"ngram\": \"the trap\", \"from\": 4180, \"to\": 4188}, {\"ngram\": \"elitism\", \"from\": 4192, \"to\": 4199}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Tennis has always had that reputation but padel is seen as more urban, and has taken off in traditionally working-class areas like Manchester.\", \"from\": 4201, \"to\": 4343, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Tennis\", \"from\": 4201, \"to\": 4207}, {\"ngram\": \"that reputation\", \"from\": 4223, \"to\": 4238}, {\"ngram\": \"padel\", \"from\": 4243, \"to\": 4248}, {\"ngram\": \"traditionally working-class areas\", \"from\": 4293, \"to\": 4326}, {\"ngram\": \"Manchester\", \"from\": 4332, \"to\": 4342}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He has teamed up with the Lawn Tennis Association and a number of other private investors to help install padel courts in schools in underprivileged areas.\", \"from\": 4345, \"to\": 4500, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4371, \"end\": 4394, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lawn_Tennis_Association\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.8929852929169271e-19, \"text\": \"Lawn Tennis Association\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lawn_Tennis_Association\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lawn_Tennis_Association\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a number\", \"from\": 4399, \"to\": 4407}, {\"ngram\": \"other private investors\", \"from\": 4411, \"to\": 4434}, {\"ngram\": \"padel courts\", \"from\": 4451, \"to\": 4463}, {\"ngram\": \"schools\", \"from\": 4467, \"to\": 4474}, {\"ngram\": \"underprivileged areas\", \"from\": 4478, \"to\": 4499}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He's also been in contact with the Mayor of Greater Manchester, Andy Burnham.\", \"from\": 4501, \"to\": 4578, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4565, \"end\": 4577, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Burnham\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Andy Burnham\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Burnham\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Burnham\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"contact\", \"from\": 4519, \"to\": 4526}, {\"ngram\": \"the Mayor\", \"from\": 4532, \"to\": 4541}, {\"ngram\": \"Greater Manchester\", \"from\": 4545, \"to\": 4563}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'I can already foresee a problem,' Manford said.\", \"from\": 4580, \"to\": 4628, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a problem\", \"from\": 4603, \"to\": 4612}, {\"ngram\": \"Manford\", \"from\": 4615, \"to\": 4622}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'I just played this morning at this lovely club in Wilmslow.\", \"from\": 4629, \"to\": 4689, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4680, \"end\": 4688, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Wilmslow_Road\", \"score\": 0.8988310252532693, \"rank\": 0.1125561667365124, \"text\": \"Wilmslow\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Wilmslow_Road\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Wilmslow_Road\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"this lovely club\", \"from\": 4660, \"to\": 4676}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\u00a311 quid each I think we all paid.\", \"from\": 4690, \"to\": 4724, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Around \\u00a344 for the court in total.\", \"from\": 4725, \"to\": 4759, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the court\", \"from\": 4740, \"to\": 4749}, {\"ngram\": \"total\", \"from\": 4753, \"to\": 4758}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I have got my \\u00a3250 racket.\", \"from\": 4760, \"to\": 4786, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"my \\u00a3250 racket\", \"from\": 4771, \"to\": 4785}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\u00a3100 trainers and my nice kit.\", \"from\": 4787, \"to\": 4817, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"\\u00a3100 trainers\", \"from\": 4787, \"to\": 4800}, {\"ngram\": \"my nice kit\", \"from\": 4805, \"to\": 4816}]}, {\"sentence\": \"All of a sudden, I am walking around with \\u00a3500 worth of stuff and I am playing with three other people who also have the privilege of having a day off.\", \"from\": 4818, \"to\": 4969, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"\\u00a3500 worth\", \"from\": 4860, \"to\": 4870}, {\"ngram\": \"stuff\", \"from\": 4874, \"to\": 4879}, {\"ngram\": \"three other people\", \"from\": 4902, \"to\": 4920}, {\"ngram\": \"the privilege\", \"from\": 4935, \"to\": 4948}, {\"ngram\": \"a day\", \"from\": 4959, \"to\": 4964}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'I am already thinking, 'Is this becoming elitist?\", \"from\": 4971, \"to\": 5021, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Is this becoming a problem?'\", \"from\": 5022, \"to\": 5050, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a problem\", \"from\": 5039, \"to\": 5048}]}, {\"sentence\": \"- because everywhere else, it's a people's sport.\", \"from\": 5051, \"to\": 5100, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a people's sport\", \"from\": 5083, \"to\": 5099}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It's the opposite of tennis in that respect.\", \"from\": 5101, \"to\": 5145, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the opposite\", \"from\": 5106, \"to\": 5118}, {\"ngram\": \"tennis\", \"from\": 5122, \"to\": 5128}, {\"ngram\": \"that respect\", \"from\": 5132, \"to\": 5144}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Tennis is all-whites, the Royal Box, make sure you wear a tie at the club and all that.\", \"from\": 5146, \"to\": 5233, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Tennis\", \"from\": 5146, \"to\": 5152}, {\"ngram\": \"-whites\", \"from\": 5159, \"to\": 5166}, {\"ngram\": \"a tie\", \"from\": 5202, \"to\": 5207}, {\"ngram\": \"the club\", \"from\": 5211, \"to\": 5219}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Padel is a bit more street, it's a bit more urban.'\", \"from\": 5234, \"to\": 5285, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Padel\", \"from\": 5234, \"to\": 5239}, {\"ngram\": \"a bit more street\", \"from\": 5243, \"to\": 5260}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Manford, who has been playing padel with the likes of England footballer Jordan Pickford, has already experienced a number of obstacles with installing courts in schools.\", \"from\": 5287, \"to\": 5457, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5341, \"end\": 5348, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/England_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.8271153672616365, \"rank\": 0.20901709002665528, \"text\": \"England\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/England_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/England_national_football_team\"}, {\"begin\": 5360, \"end\": 5375, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jordan_Pickford\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Jordan Pickford\", \"types\": [\"Q937857\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jordan_Pickford\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jordan_Pickford\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Manford\", \"from\": 5287, \"to\": 5294}, {\"ngram\": \"padel\", \"from\": 5317, \"to\": 5322}, {\"ngram\": \"the likes\", \"from\": 5328, \"to\": 5337}, {\"ngram\": \"a number\", \"from\": 5401, \"to\": 5409}, {\"ngram\": \"obstacles\", \"from\": 5413, \"to\": 5422}, {\"ngram\": \"courts\", \"from\": 5439, \"to\": 5445}, {\"ngram\": \"schools\", \"from\": 5449, \"to\": 5456}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He needs to convince private investors that it's worth their money.\", \"from\": 5458, \"to\": 5525, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"private investors\", \"from\": 5479, \"to\": 5496}, {\"ngram\": \"their money\", \"from\": 5513, \"to\": 5524}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He also requires brands like Castore and Babolat to back his big ideas.\", \"from\": 5526, \"to\": 5597, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"brands\", \"from\": 5543, \"to\": 5549}, {\"ngram\": \"Castore\", \"from\": 5555, \"to\": 5562}, {\"ngram\": \"Babolat\", \"from\": 5567, \"to\": 5574}, {\"ngram\": \"his big ideas\", \"from\": 5583, \"to\": 5596}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'It's an absolute ball****, to be perfectly honest,' the comedian explained.\", \"from\": 5599, \"to\": 5675, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"an absolute ball\", \"from\": 5605, \"to\": 5621}, {\"ngram\": \"the comedian\", \"from\": 5652, \"to\": 5664}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'I thought it would be a doddle.\", \"from\": 5676, \"to\": 5708, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a doddle\", \"from\": 5699, \"to\": 5707}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Just the red tape of it.\", \"from\": 5709, \"to\": 5733, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Just the red tape\", \"from\": 5709, \"to\": 5726}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The only way to make this viable is I will pay for three padel courts plus all the work that goes around it.\", \"from\": 5734, \"to\": 5842, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The only way\", \"from\": 5734, \"to\": 5746}, {\"ngram\": \"three padel courts\", \"from\": 5785, \"to\": 5803}, {\"ngram\": \"all the work\", \"from\": 5809, \"to\": 5821}]}, {\"sentence\": \"You are talking \\u00a3150,000 for three courts on a school field.\", \"from\": 5843, \"to\": 5903, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"three courts\", \"from\": 5872, \"to\": 5884}, {\"ngram\": \"a school field\", \"from\": 5888, \"to\": 5902}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'A lot of these school grounds are massive and underused.\", \"from\": 5905, \"to\": 5962, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"A lot\", \"from\": 5906, \"to\": 5911}, {\"ngram\": \"these school grounds\", \"from\": 5915, \"to\": 5935}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The grass is either rock solid or soaking wet, unusable for four to five months a year.\", \"from\": 5963, \"to\": 6050, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The grass\", \"from\": 5963, \"to\": 5972}, {\"ngram\": \"four to five months\", \"from\": 6023, \"to\": 6042}]}, {\"sentence\": \"What I am saying is, \\\"Give me this land for free for 25 years and I will build you three padel courts, we will fence it all off so it becomes its own entity, you have access to it, they are yours, the kids can use them for PE and lunchtime clubs and afterschool clubs\\\".\", \"from\": 6051, \"to\": 6320, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 6274, \"end\": 6276, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Physical_education\", \"score\": 0.9999987726149159, \"rank\": 1.2272120368375012e-06, \"text\": \"PE\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Physical_education\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Physical_education\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"this land\", \"from\": 6081, \"to\": 6090}, {\"ngram\": \"25 years\", \"from\": 6104, \"to\": 6112}, {\"ngram\": \"three padel courts\", \"from\": 6134, \"to\": 6152}, {\"ngram\": \"its own entity\", \"from\": 6193, \"to\": 6207}, {\"ngram\": \"access\", \"from\": 6218, \"to\": 6224}, {\"ngram\": \"the kids\", \"from\": 6248, \"to\": 6256}, {\"ngram\": \"afterschool clubs\", \"from\": 6301, \"to\": 6318}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But then what we also do is rent them out on weekends, evenings and school holidays.\", \"from\": 6321, \"to\": 6405, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"weekends\", \"from\": 6366, \"to\": 6374}, {\"ngram\": \"evenings\", \"from\": 6376, \"to\": 6384}, {\"ngram\": \"school holidays\", \"from\": 6389, \"to\": 6404}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'So they sort of end up paying for themselves over time.\", \"from\": 6407, \"to\": 6463, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"time\", \"from\": 6458, \"to\": 6462}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Hopefully, what ends up happening thenis that you could then invest in more padel courts in more schools.\", \"from\": 6464, \"to\": 6569, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"thenis\", \"from\": 6498, \"to\": 6504}, {\"ngram\": \"more padel courts\", \"from\": 6535, \"to\": 6552}, {\"ngram\": \"more schools\", \"from\": 6556, \"to\": 6568}]}, {\"sentence\": \"You will never run out of schools that need them.\", \"from\": 6570, \"to\": 6619, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"schools\", \"from\": 6596, \"to\": 6603}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'What I am trying to say to these investors is, \\\"Do not come asking for your money back in a years' time\\\" - that's not what this is.\", \"from\": 6621, \"to\": 6753, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"these investors\", \"from\": 6649, \"to\": 6664}, {\"ngram\": \"your money\", \"from\": 6693, \"to\": 6703}, {\"ngram\": \"a years' time\", \"from\": 6712, \"to\": 6725}]}, {\"sentence\": \"This is more about creating a legacy in padel, can we give underprivileged children an opportunity to play this brilliant sport?\", \"from\": 6754, \"to\": 6882, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a legacy\", \"from\": 6782, \"to\": 6790}, {\"ngram\": \"padel\", \"from\": 6794, \"to\": 6799}, {\"ngram\": \"underprivileged children\", \"from\": 6813, \"to\": 6837}, {\"ngram\": \"an opportunity\", \"from\": 6838, \"to\": 6852}, {\"ngram\": \"this brilliant sport\", \"from\": 6861, \"to\": 6881}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Can we give underprivileged children an opportunity to play this brilliant sport?\", \"from\": 6884, \"to\": 6965, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"underprivileged children\", \"from\": 6896, \"to\": 6920}, {\"ngram\": \"an opportunity\", \"from\": 6921, \"to\": 6935}, {\"ngram\": \"this brilliant sport\", \"from\": 6944, \"to\": 6964}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'You can not just build a court and leave it.\", \"from\": 6967, \"to\": 7012, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a court\", \"from\": 6991, \"to\": 6998}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I am speaking to Castore about clothing.\", \"from\": 7013, \"to\": 7053, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 7030, \"end\": 7037, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Castore_(brand)\", \"score\": 0.9341150516593708, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Castore\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Castore_(brand)\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Castore_(brand)\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"clothing\", \"from\": 7044, \"to\": 7052}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I am speaking to Babolat about rackets.\", \"from\": 7054, \"to\": 7093, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 7071, \"end\": 7078, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Babolat\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Babolat\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Babolat\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Babolat\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"rackets\", \"from\": 7085, \"to\": 7092}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I have been speaking to the LTA about up-skilling PE teachers.\", \"from\": 7094, \"to\": 7156, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 7144, \"end\": 7146, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Physical_education\", \"score\": 0.9999987726149159, \"rank\": 1.2272120368375012e-06, \"text\": \"PE\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Physical_education\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Physical_education\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the LTA\", \"from\": 7118, \"to\": 7125}]}, {\"sentence\": \"If we just build three courts and leave it, and the kids just play it in PE and never again, then you have failed.\", \"from\": 7157, \"to\": 7271, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 7230, \"end\": 7232, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Physical_education\", \"score\": 0.9999987726149159, \"rank\": 1.2272120368375012e-06, \"text\": \"PE\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Physical_education\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Physical_education\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"three courts\", \"from\": 7174, \"to\": 7186}, {\"ngram\": \"the kids\", \"from\": 7205, \"to\": 7213}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'These companies\\u2026 I said to the guys at Babolat, I got a pair of Nikes when I was 10, I am 43 now and I probably spend \\u00a3700 a year on Nike trainers.\", \"from\": 7273, \"to\": 7421, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 7313, \"end\": 7320, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Babolat\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Babolat\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Babolat\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Babolat\"}, {\"begin\": 7338, \"end\": 7343, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nike,_Inc.\", \"score\": 0.9378551719603833, \"rank\": 0.0625999686372717, \"text\": \"Nikes\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nike,_Inc.\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nike,_Inc.\"}, {\"begin\": 7407, \"end\": 7411, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/MIM-3_Nike_Ajax\", \"score\": 0.9997238048146531, \"rank\": 0.0002762714898265016, \"text\": \"Nike\", \"types\": [\"Q728\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/MIM-3_Nike_Ajax\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/MIM-3_Nike_Ajax\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the guys\", \"from\": 7301, \"to\": 7309}, {\"ngram\": \"a pair\", \"from\": 7328, \"to\": 7334}]}, {\"sentence\": \"So we all know from a company POV, if you can get a Castore t-shirt or a Babalot racket or whatever it is onto a kid at 10 or 11, they are going to stick with that brand for a long time.\", \"from\": 7422, \"to\": 7608, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 7452, \"end\": 7455, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Narration\", \"score\": 0.9999999985766408, \"rank\": 1.1769384709051675e-09, \"text\": \"POV\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Narration\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Narration\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a company\", \"from\": 7442, \"to\": 7451}, {\"ngram\": \"a Castore t-shirt\", \"from\": 7472, \"to\": 7489}, {\"ngram\": \"a Babalot racket\", \"from\": 7493, \"to\": 7509}, {\"ngram\": \"whatever\", \"from\": 7513, \"to\": 7521}, {\"ngram\": \"a kid\", \"from\": 7533, \"to\": 7538}, {\"ngram\": \"that brand\", \"from\": 7581, \"to\": 7591}, {\"ngram\": \"a long time\", \"from\": 7596, \"to\": 7607}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'That's what I am telling these companies and telling them to get behind me.\", \"from\": 7610, \"to\": 7686, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"these companies\", \"from\": 7636, \"to\": 7651}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Help me get these kids to feel like this sport is for them and that it's not elitist.'\", \"from\": 7687, \"to\": 7773, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"these kids\", \"from\": 7699, \"to\": 7709}, {\"ngram\": \"this sport\", \"from\": 7723, \"to\": 7733}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Manford has a padel dream.\", \"from\": 7775, \"to\": 7801, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Manford\", \"from\": 7775, \"to\": 7782}, {\"ngram\": \"a padel dream\", \"from\": 7787, \"to\": 7800}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He wantsTeam GBto compete in the sport at the 2032Olympic Gamesin Brisbane, but that would appear some way off given the lack of representation at the recent youth championships.\", \"from\": 7802, \"to\": 7980, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the sport\", \"from\": 7831, \"to\": 7840}, {\"ngram\": \"the 2032Olympic Gamesin Brisbane\", \"from\": 7844, \"to\": 7876}, {\"ngram\": \"the lack\", \"from\": 7919, \"to\": 7927}, {\"ngram\": \"representation\", \"from\": 7931, \"to\": 7945}, {\"ngram\": \"the recent youth championships\", \"from\": 7949, \"to\": 7979}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'The LTA did not embrace it as early as they should have,' said De Haan explaining Team GB's absence.\", \"from\": 7982, \"to\": 8083, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 7987, \"end\": 7990, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lawn_Tennis_Association\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 7.81330921053578e-25, \"text\": \"LTA\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lawn_Tennis_Association\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lawn_Tennis_Association\"}, {\"begin\": 8046, \"end\": 8053, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Foppe_de_Haan\", \"score\": 0.9999999984229362, \"rank\": 1.577465222813358e-09, \"text\": \"De Haan\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q628099\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Foppe_de_Haan\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Foppe_de_Haan\"}, {\"begin\": 8065, \"end\": 8072, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_GB\", \"score\": 0.9999859486575087, \"rank\": 1.0241568148251358e-05, \"text\": \"Team GB\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_GB\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_GB\"}], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"'Now they are very in on the whole padel idea.\", \"from\": 8084, \"to\": 8130, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the whole padel idea\", \"from\": 8109, \"to\": 8129}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I think they saw it as direct competition to tennis, so it was snubbed off to begin with.'\", \"from\": 8131, \"to\": 8221, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"direct competition\", \"from\": 8154, \"to\": 8172}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It should also be noted that padel is not currently an Olympic sport - and is not on the schedule for Los Angeles 2028 - but it could be included four years later if this global boom continues which, if the LTA's ambitious plan is anything to go by, looks likely.\", \"from\": 8223, \"to\": 8486, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 8325, \"end\": 8341, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2028_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Los Angeles 2028\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2028_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2028_Summer_Olympics\"}, {\"begin\": 8430, \"end\": 8433, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lawn_Tennis_Association\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 7.81330921053578e-25, \"text\": \"LTA\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lawn_Tennis_Association\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lawn_Tennis_Association\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"padel\", \"from\": 8252, \"to\": 8257}, {\"ngram\": \"an Olympic sport\", \"from\": 8275, \"to\": 8291}, {\"ngram\": \"the schedule\", \"from\": 8308, \"to\": 8320}, {\"ngram\": \"this global boom\", \"from\": 8389, \"to\": 8405}, {\"ngram\": \"anything\", \"from\": 8454, \"to\": 8462}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Lofty targets include growing the visibility of padel to increase awareness from 20% to 40% of the population and interest in playing from 7.5% to 15% and boost participation.\", \"from\": 8488, \"to\": 8663, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Lofty targets\", \"from\": 8488, \"to\": 8501}, {\"ngram\": \"the visibility\", \"from\": 8518, \"to\": 8532}, {\"ngram\": \"padel\", \"from\": 8536, \"to\": 8541}, {\"ngram\": \"awareness\", \"from\": 8554, \"to\": 8563}, {\"ngram\": \"20% to 40%\", \"from\": 8569, \"to\": 8579}, {\"ngram\": \"the population\", \"from\": 8583, \"to\": 8597}, {\"ngram\": \"interest\", \"from\": 8602, \"to\": 8610}, {\"ngram\": \"participation\", \"from\": 8649, \"to\": 8662}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The LTA also hopes to increase the number of annual padel players from 129,000 to 400,000 and build another 650 courts to ensure there are 1,000 in total around the UK.\", \"from\": 8665, \"to\": 8833, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 8669, \"end\": 8672, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lawn_Tennis_Association\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 7.81330921053578e-25, \"text\": \"LTA\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lawn_Tennis_Association\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lawn_Tennis_Association\"}, {\"begin\": 8830, \"end\": 8832, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/COVID-19_pandemic_in_the_United_Kingdom\", \"score\": 0.9999993750245401, \"rank\": 6.249761859456696e-07, \"text\": \"UK\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/COVID-19_pandemic_in_the_United_Kingdom\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/COVID-19_pandemic_in_the_United_Kingdom\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the number\", \"from\": 8696, \"to\": 8706}, {\"ngram\": \"annual padel players\", \"from\": 8710, \"to\": 8730}, {\"ngram\": \"another 650 courts\", \"from\": 8765, \"to\": 8783}, {\"ngram\": \"total\", \"from\": 8813, \"to\": 8818}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'Can we look forward to the 2032 Brisbane Olympics, and could one of the kids that plays padel on one of those courts make it in eight years' time and play for Team GB?'\", \"from\": 8835, \"to\": 9004, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 8868, \"end\": 8876, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brisbane\", \"score\": 0.9999999999990905, \"rank\": 2.972031720768455e-13, \"text\": \"Brisbane\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brisbane\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brisbane\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the kids\", \"from\": 8904, \"to\": 8912}, {\"ngram\": \"padel\", \"from\": 8924, \"to\": 8929}, {\"ngram\": \"those courts\", \"from\": 8940, \"to\": 8952}, {\"ngram\": \"eight years' time\", \"from\": 8964, \"to\": 8981}, {\"ngram\": \"Team GB\", \"from\": 8995, \"to\": 9002}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Manford asked.\", \"from\": 9005, \"to\": 9019, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Manford\", \"from\": 9005, \"to\": 9012}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'That would be the dream.\", \"from\": 9021, \"to\": 9046, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the dream\", \"from\": 9036, \"to\": 9045}]}, {\"sentence\": \"From not entering a team in the youth world championships to eight years later having a team at the Olympics, that would be an incredible legacy.'\", \"from\": 9047, \"to\": 9193, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a team\", \"from\": 9065, \"to\": 9071}, {\"ngram\": \"the youth world\", \"from\": 9075, \"to\": 9090}, {\"ngram\": \"a team\", \"from\": 9133, \"to\": 9139}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympics\", \"from\": 9143, \"to\": 9155}, {\"ngram\": \"an incredible legacy\", \"from\": 9171, \"to\": 9191}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Padel has surged in popularity - but the UK must be careful to avoid the same mistakes seen in Sweden - where they overinvested and built too many courts.\", \"from\": 9195, \"to\": 9349, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 9236, \"end\": 9238, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/COVID-19_pandemic_in_the_United_Kingdom\", \"score\": 0.9999993750245401, \"rank\": 6.249761859456696e-07, \"text\": \"UK\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/COVID-19_pandemic_in_the_United_Kingdom\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/COVID-19_pandemic_in_the_United_Kingdom\"}, {\"begin\": 9290, \"end\": 9296, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sweden\", \"score\": 0.9999999999972715, \"rank\": 2.5849076364242742e-12, \"text\": \"Sweden\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sweden\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sweden\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Padel\", \"from\": 9195, \"to\": 9200}, {\"ngram\": \"popularity\", \"from\": 9215, \"to\": 9225}, {\"ngram\": \"the same mistakes\", \"from\": 9264, \"to\": 9281}, {\"ngram\": \"too many courts\", \"from\": 9333, \"to\": 9348}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Gordon, the Swede who just opened Rocket Padel in Battersea, explains how things went wrong in his home country and how Britain can avoid similar issues.\", \"from\": 9351, \"to\": 9504, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 9351, \"end\": 9357, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mike_Gordon\", \"score\": 0.8877413606615441, \"rank\": 0.1264542176155043, \"text\": \"Gordon\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q483501\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mike_Gordon\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mike_Gordon\"}, {\"begin\": 9392, \"end\": 9397, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Padel_(sport)\", \"score\": 0.9869493094630484, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Padel\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Padel_(sport)\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Padel_(sport)\"}, {\"begin\": 9401, \"end\": 9410, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Battersea\", \"score\": 0.9999903353776519, \"rank\": 9.646315286896063e-06, \"text\": \"Battersea\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Battersea\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Battersea\"}, {\"begin\": 9471, \"end\": 9478, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"score\": 0.9999999912979547, \"rank\": 8.702109061298177e-09, \"text\": \"Britain\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the Swede\", \"from\": 9359, \"to\": 9368}, {\"ngram\": \"things\", \"from\": 9425, \"to\": 9431}, {\"ngram\": \"his home country\", \"from\": 9446, \"to\": 9462}, {\"ngram\": \"similar issues\", \"from\": 9489, \"to\": 9503}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'Padel sort of exploded in Sweden during Covid,' Gordon said.\", \"from\": 9506, \"to\": 9567, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 9533, \"end\": 9539, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sweden\", \"score\": 0.9999999999972715, \"rank\": 2.5849076364242742e-12, \"text\": \"Sweden\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sweden\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sweden\"}, {\"begin\": 9555, \"end\": 9561, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mike_Gordon\", \"score\": 0.8877413606615441, \"rank\": 0.1264542176155043, \"text\": \"Gordon\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q483501\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mike_Gordon\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mike_Gordon\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Padel\", \"from\": 9507, \"to\": 9512}, {\"ngram\": \"Covid\", \"from\": 9547, \"to\": 9552}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'It was one of the few sports you were allowed to play with fishing and golf.\", \"from\": 9568, \"to\": 9645, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the few sports\", \"from\": 9583, \"to\": 9597}, {\"ngram\": \"fishing\", \"from\": 9628, \"to\": 9635}, {\"ngram\": \"golf\", \"from\": 9640, \"to\": 9644}]}, {\"sentence\": \"And golf is not so easy in Sweden with the weather!\", \"from\": 9646, \"to\": 9697, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 9673, \"end\": 9679, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sweden\", \"score\": 0.9999999999972715, \"rank\": 2.5849076364242742e-12, \"text\": \"Sweden\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sweden\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sweden\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"golf\", \"from\": 9650, \"to\": 9654}, {\"ngram\": \"the weather\", \"from\": 9685, \"to\": 9696}]}, {\"sentence\": \"We opened up a few other clubs, the market then got oversaturated in Sweden, so we learned a lot from that.\", \"from\": 9698, \"to\": 9805, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 9767, \"end\": 9773, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sweden\", \"score\": 0.9999999999972715, \"rank\": 2.5849076364242742e-12, \"text\": \"Sweden\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sweden\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sweden\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a few other clubs\", \"from\": 9711, \"to\": 9728}, {\"ngram\": \"the market\", \"from\": 9730, \"to\": 9740}, {\"ngram\": \"a lot\", \"from\": 9789, \"to\": 9794}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'Given the population, we built 4,000 courts over two years, that was too much.\", \"from\": 9807, \"to\": 9886, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the population\", \"from\": 9814, \"to\": 9828}, {\"ngram\": \"4,000 courts\", \"from\": 9839, \"to\": 9851}, {\"ngram\": \"two years\", \"from\": 9857, \"to\": 9866}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But if you look at the sport today\\u2026 The ones situated in the right places are full.\", \"from\": 9887, \"to\": 9970, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the sport\", \"from\": 9906, \"to\": 9915}, {\"ngram\": \"The ones\", \"from\": 9923, \"to\": 9931}, {\"ngram\": \"the right places\", \"from\": 9944, \"to\": 9960}]}, {\"sentence\": \"So they are doing pretty good.\", \"from\": 9971, \"to\": 10001, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"'To come back to the learning, one of the main things we are doing here in the UK that I can take advantage of is that we are focusing a lot on activities and to build from the ground up with a foundation in a youth academy, activating box leagues and getting people to compete so they feel they keep developing.\", \"from\": 10003, \"to\": 10315, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 10082, \"end\": 10084, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/COVID-19_pandemic_in_the_United_Kingdom\", \"score\": 0.9999993750245401, \"rank\": 6.249761859456696e-07, \"text\": \"UK\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/COVID-19_pandemic_in_the_United_Kingdom\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/COVID-19_pandemic_in_the_United_Kingdom\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the learning\", \"from\": 10020, \"to\": 10032}, {\"ngram\": \"the main things\", \"from\": 10041, \"to\": 10056}, {\"ngram\": \"advantage\", \"from\": 10101, \"to\": 10110}, {\"ngram\": \"a lot\", \"from\": 10138, \"to\": 10143}, {\"ngram\": \"activities\", \"from\": 10147, \"to\": 10157}, {\"ngram\": \"the ground\", \"from\": 10176, \"to\": 10186}, {\"ngram\": \"a foundation\", \"from\": 10195, \"to\": 10207}, {\"ngram\": \"a youth academy\", \"from\": 10211, \"to\": 10226}, {\"ngram\": \"box leagues\", \"from\": 10239, \"to\": 10250}, {\"ngram\": \"people\", \"from\": 10263, \"to\": 10269}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'In Sweden, you could open a club and it would get full, but people [running them] got lazy.\", \"from\": 10317, \"to\": 10409, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 10321, \"end\": 10327, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sweden\", \"score\": 0.9999999999972715, \"rank\": 2.5849076364242742e-12, \"text\": \"Sweden\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sweden\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sweden\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a club\", \"from\": 10344, \"to\": 10350}, {\"ngram\": \"people\", \"from\": 10378, \"to\": 10384}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Most of the operators were fat cats.\", \"from\": 10410, \"to\": 10446, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the operators\", \"from\": 10418, \"to\": 10431}, {\"ngram\": \"fat cats\", \"from\": 10437, \"to\": 10445}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The clubs were full and they were making money, so they felt they did not need to do anything else.\", \"from\": 10447, \"to\": 10546, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The clubs\", \"from\": 10447, \"to\": 10456}, {\"ngram\": \"money\", \"from\": 10488, \"to\": 10493}, {\"ngram\": \"anything\", \"from\": 10532, \"to\": 10540}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'The clubs in Sweden that survived and are doing good are the ones that opened pre-Covid and started early with kids, academies, running tournaments, social media, which helps too.\", \"from\": 10548, \"to\": 10728, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 10562, \"end\": 10568, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sweden\", \"score\": 0.9999999999972715, \"rank\": 2.5849076364242742e-12, \"text\": \"Sweden\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sweden\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sweden\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The clubs\", \"from\": 10549, \"to\": 10558}, {\"ngram\": \"good\", \"from\": 10597, \"to\": 10601}, {\"ngram\": \"the ones\", \"from\": 10606, \"to\": 10614}, {\"ngram\": \"kids\", \"from\": 10660, \"to\": 10664}]}, {\"sentence\": \"A little bit more than just padel.\", \"from\": 10729, \"to\": 10763, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"just padel\", \"from\": 10752, \"to\": 10762}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It can be a bar, a restaurant, showing Premier League games or Formula One.\", \"from\": 10764, \"to\": 10839, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a bar\", \"from\": 10774, \"to\": 10779}, {\"ngram\": \"a restaurant\", \"from\": 10781, \"to\": 10793}, {\"ngram\": \"Premier League games\", \"from\": 10803, \"to\": 10823}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Those are the clubs that are doing well.'\", \"from\": 10840, \"to\": 10881, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the clubs\", \"from\": 10850, \"to\": 10859}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The two most common complaints about padel are that the shots are too loud - sounding a little like gunfire - and that it's too hard to get four people together for a doubles match.\", \"from\": 10883, \"to\": 11064, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The two most common complaints\", \"from\": 10883, \"to\": 10913}, {\"ngram\": \"padel\", \"from\": 10920, \"to\": 10925}, {\"ngram\": \"the shots\", \"from\": 10935, \"to\": 10944}, {\"ngram\": \"gunfire\", \"from\": 10983, \"to\": 10990}, {\"ngram\": \"four people\", \"from\": 11023, \"to\": 11034}, {\"ngram\": \"a doubles match\", \"from\": 11048, \"to\": 11063}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But the sport has moved quickly to address those concerns.\", \"from\": 11065, \"to\": 11123, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the sport\", \"from\": 11069, \"to\": 11078}, {\"ngram\": \"those concerns\", \"from\": 11108, \"to\": 11122}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'It is kind of noisy with outdoor courts,' Gordon admits.\", \"from\": 11125, \"to\": 11182, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 11168, \"end\": 11174, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mike_Gordon\", \"score\": 0.8877413606615441, \"rank\": 0.1264542176155043, \"text\": \"Gordon\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q483501\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mike_Gordon\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mike_Gordon\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"outdoor courts\", \"from\": 11151, \"to\": 11165}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'[But] at Rocket Padel, we are only opening indoor courts.\", \"from\": 11183, \"to\": 11241, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Rocket Padel\", \"from\": 11193, \"to\": 11205}, {\"ngram\": \"indoor courts\", \"from\": 11227, \"to\": 11240}]}, {\"sentence\": \"We invest money and attention into using materials that are sound-reducing.\", \"from\": 11242, \"to\": 11317, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"money\", \"from\": 11252, \"to\": 11257}, {\"ngram\": \"attention\", \"from\": 11262, \"to\": 11271}, {\"ngram\": \"materials\", \"from\": 11283, \"to\": 11292}]}, {\"sentence\": \"At one of our clubs, we actually extended the wall to make it thicker and keep the sound inside.'\", \"from\": 11318, \"to\": 11415, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"our clubs\", \"from\": 11328, \"to\": 11337}, {\"ngram\": \"the wall\", \"from\": 11360, \"to\": 11368}, {\"ngram\": \"the sound\", \"from\": 11397, \"to\": 11406}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Meanwhile, the rise of a new app - Playtomic - has made it a lot easier for padel players to assemble for doubles matches.\", \"from\": 11417, \"to\": 11539, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the rise\", \"from\": 11428, \"to\": 11436}, {\"ngram\": \"a new app - Playtomic\", \"from\": 11440, \"to\": 11461}, {\"ngram\": \"padel players\", \"from\": 11493, \"to\": 11506}, {\"ngram\": \"doubles matches\", \"from\": 11523, \"to\": 11538}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'We tackle that issue in our club with a WhatsApp group, and we also use the Playtomic app,' De Haan added.\", \"from\": 11541, \"to\": 11648, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 11582, \"end\": 11590, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/WhatsApp\", \"score\": 0.9811910366193594, \"rank\": 0.01916952222176099, \"text\": \"WhatsApp\", \"types\": [\"Q7397\", \"Q386724\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/WhatsApp\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/WhatsApp\"}, {\"begin\": 11634, \"end\": 11641, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Foppe_de_Haan\", \"score\": 0.9999999984229362, \"rank\": 1.577465222813358e-09, \"text\": \"De Haan\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q628099\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Foppe_de_Haan\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Foppe_de_Haan\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngr